                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-95-defend933 t17960914-95-punish540"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
